00:07:49.799 --> 00:07:55.880
So as part of that project intake, there's a key section here called evaluation metrics. And right

00:07:55.880 --> 00:08:00.600
off the bat, you should have a good idea of whether you're trying to address mortality,

00:08:00.600 --> 00:08:05.880
admission, length of stay, financial issues, or human effort generally across the types of

00:08:05.880 --> 00:08:09.959
problems you want to solve in the hospital. There's not a box other, which is usually an

