now in this cell. So I'm using the binomial distribution. If you're not familiar or you're

00:14:30.039 --> 00:14:36.200
not comfortable using these likelihood functions, I think this is something just really worth

00:14:36.200 --> 00:14:43.559
leaning into. A lot of abstract statistics become really concrete and intuitive once you

